## ğŸ‘¤ Threat Actor Types

- **Advanced Persistent Threats (APTs)** â€“ Sophisticated, long-term network infiltration  
- **Insider Threats** â€“ Abuse internal access; sabotage, leaks, or espionage  
- **Hacktivists** â€“ Politically or socially motivated  
- **Unskilled Threat Actors** â€“ Script kiddies, revenge actors, hobbyists  
- **Hacker Categories**:
  - **Ethical Hackers** â€“ Work within the law (a.k.a. white hats)
  - **Semi-authorised Researchers** â€“ Probe but donâ€™t exploit
  - **Unethical Hackers** â€“ Malicious, motivated by profit or chaos

